description:
Featuring footage from:
Spider-Man 2 (2004)
Star Wars Episode 3: Revenge of the Sith (2005)

This is also my submission for @NeverthinkTVs meme jam 6 of which the topic is "Spider-Man"

J Jonah Jameson fires Anakin Skywalker after he doesn't give him the photos he wanted, Anakin is outraged as a result. This meme combines the prequel meme about Anakin getting denied the rank of master by Mace Windu and the Raimi JJJ laughing meme.

If you like what you see be sure to like, comment, share and subscribe!

#RevengeOfTheSith
